<input type="hidden" name="course" value="problemset">
<input type="hidden" name="task" value="1753">
Given a string and a pattern, your task is to count the number of positions where the pattern occurs in the string.<br />
<br />
<b id="input">Input</b><br />
<br />
The first input line has a string of length $n$, and the second input line has a pattern of length $m$. Both of them consist of characters aâ€“z.<br />
<br />
<b id="output">Output</b><br />
<br />
Print one integer: the number of occurrences.<br />
<br />
<b id="constraints">Constraints</b><br />
<ul>
<li>$1 \le n,m \le 10^6$<br />
</ul>
<b id="example">Example</b><br />
<br />
Input:<br />
<code>saippuakauppias<br />
pp</code><br />
<br />
Output:<br />
<code>2</code>    </div>
